original_title: Kira Soltanovich: You Did This to Me
overview: Hormone crazed and pregnant Kira Soltanovich gets real with the trials and tribulations of pregnancy, birthing and raising kids. Putting her belly on the line, she hones in her maternal instincts in this hard-hitting, labor of love comedy special.
title: Kira Soltanovich: You Did This to Me
